Package db

Contains classes responsible for interacting with database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveUserService
    This class is responsible for interacting with table containing active users in database.
    AppDictionaryService
    This class is responsible for interacting with table containing app constances in database.
    Database
    This is a singleton class initializing EntityManager.
    PasswordService
    This class is responsible for interacting with table containing passwords in database.
    UserService
    This class is responsible for interacting with table containing all ever signed up users in database.
    WordService
    This class is responsible for interacting with table containing words to guess in database.

Package db Description

Contains classes responsible for interacting with database. Every class, here called service, is associated with a table in database. All the services are singleton and they are meant to be injected as a field whenever they are needed.
